 party</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Scout or guide group</td>\n      <td>The assistant county/area commissioner or someone from Association Headquarters</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Football or rugby club</td>\n      <td>Someone from the local football association or the league chairperson or secretary</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Swimming or judo clubs</td>\n      <td>Someone from their national headquarters</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Youth orchestras, choirs etc</td>\n      <td>Someone from their local education authority, or vicar for church groups</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Army or Airforce cadets</td>\n      <td>Their commanding officer or someone from their services authority</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Clubs or youth clubs</td>\n      <td>Someone from the local authority where they&rsquo;re registered, or their national headquarters</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Registered charities</td>\n      <td>The director or a person in a similar position in the organisation</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>If the group is going abroad to perform for any purpose (including sports competitions) the letter must say:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>all members of the group are amateurs</li>\n  <li>they won&rsquo;t get any payment</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/@travel/documents/digitalasset/dg_174926.pdf\" title=\"Download 'Example supporting letter' (PDF, 56KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘Example supporting letter’ (PDF, 56KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>If there are children from more than one organisation travelling, you need to send a supporting letter from each organisation.</p>\n</div>\n\n"},{"web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/collective-group-passports/getting-the-passport-changed","slug":"getting-the-passport-changed","order":5,"title":"Getting the passport changed","body"